  <!-- TIMELINE -->
  <section id="timeline" style="background:var(--bg);padding:40px 0 28px;">
    <div style="padding:0 8vw 32px;">
      <div class="section-tag reveal">The Journey</div>
      <div class="section-title reveal">Season<br><span>Chronicle</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chr-scroll reveal" id="chr-scroll">
      <div class="chr-track" id="chr-track">

        <div class="chr-card chr-silver">
          <div class="chr-icon">🦁</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2008</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--silver">Debut</div>
          <div class="chr-title">The Beginning</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Chennai Super Kings make their IPL debut and reach the final in their very first season,
            launching a legendary era.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-semi">
          <div class="chr-icon">💛</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2009</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--semi">Playoffs</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Passion Grows</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A challenging season playing under tough conditions in South Africa, but the Yellow
            Army's passion continues to grow.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-win">
          <div class="chr-icon">🏆</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2010</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--win">Champions</div>
          <div class="chr-title">History Created</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">History created! CSK win their first IPL title and later lift the Champions League T20
            trophy in South Africa.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-win">
          <div class="chr-icon">👑</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2011</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--win">Champions</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Back-to-Back</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Back-to-back IPL champions. CSK become the first team to defend an IPL title and also
            reach the Champions League final.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-silver">
          <div class="chr-icon">🔥</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2012</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--silver">Runners-Up</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Finals Again</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Another IPL final appearance, proving CSK's extreme consistency and dominance on the
            biggest stage.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-silver">
          <div class="chr-icon">⚡</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2013</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--silver">Runners-Up</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Playoff Streak</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A fourth consecutive playoff qualification and another run to the IPL final. The Yellow
            Army stays dominant.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-clt">
          <div class="chr-icon">🌍🏆</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2014</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--clt">CLT20</div>
          <div class="chr-title">World Conquest</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">CSK conquer the world again by winning their second Champions League T20 title with
            supreme cricket.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-silver">
          <div class="chr-icon">💪</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2015</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--silver">Runners-Up</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Consistency</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Reach yet another IPL final, cementing their reputation as the league's most consistent
            franchise.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-ban">
          <div class="chr-icon">⏸️</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2016-17</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--ban">Paused</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Pause in Journey</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A temporary pause in the journey, but the Yellow Army never stops believing and Whistle
            Podu chants echo globally.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-win">
          <div class="chr-icon">💛🏆</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2018</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--win">Champions</div>
          <div class="chr-title">The Great Return</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">The Great Return. CSK make a dream comeback and lift their third IPL trophy, silencing
            critics in style.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-silver">
          <div class="chr-icon"> 🟡</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2019</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--silver">Runners-Up</div>
          <div class="chr-title">One Run Away</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Fall just one run short of another title in one of the closest and most dramatic IPL
            finals ever played.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-semi">
          <div class="chr-icon">🌱</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2020</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--semi">Transition</div>
          <div class="chr-title">New Beginning</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A difficult season in the UAE that sparks the beginning of a new chapter and squad
            evaluation.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-win">
          <div class="chr-icon">🏆</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2021</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--win">Champions</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Bounce Back</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">CSK bounce back in style and win their fourth IPL championship, proving their class once
            again.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-semi">
          <div class="chr-icon">🔄</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2022</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--semi">Rebuild</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Squad Rebuild</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A transition year focused on blooding fresh talent and rebuilding the squad for
            long-term future.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-win">
          <div class="chr-icon">⭐🏆</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2023</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--win">Champions</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Final Over Magic</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Final Over Magic. CSK win their fifth IPL title, equalling the record for most IPL
            championships.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-semi">
          <div class="chr-icon">🧢</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2024</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--semi">New Era</div>
          <div class="chr-title">New Leadership</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">A new era begins as leadership transitions beyond MS Dhoni to Ruturaj Gaikwad while the
            core legacy continues.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-semi">
          <div class="chr-icon">🚀</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2025</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--semi">The Hunt</div>
          <div class="chr-title">Culture & Spirit</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Fresh talent and experienced stars carry forward the CSK culture, raising the team's
            fighting spirit.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="chr-card chr-now">
          <div class="chr-icon">💛</div>
          <div class="chr-year">2026</div>
          <div class="chr-badge chr-badge--now">Legacy</div>
          <div class="chr-title">18 Year Legacy</div>
          <div class="chr-desc">Eighteen years of legacy, passion, and excellence. CSK remains one of cricket's most
            iconic franchises.</div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="chr-hint"
        style="text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:16px;opacity:0.6;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">
        ← Swipe or drag to view our 18-year journey →</div>
    </div>
